        "zh": "1. 基本概念<br>2. 記憶體架構<br>3. 指令集<br>4. 輸入/輸出<br>5. 中斷架構<br>6. 計時器<br>7. A/D轉換器<br>8. CCP<br>9. WDT<br>10. 應用實驗",
        "en": "1. Basic concept<br>2. Memory structure<br>3. Instruction set<br>4. Input/Output<br>5. Interrupt structure<br>6. Timer<br>7. A/D converter<br>8. CCP<br>9. WDT<br>10. Application experiment"
